---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="服务条款 - VibeWeave" description="VibeWeave 服务条款">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 sm:py-24">
    <a href="/" class="mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-[var(--vw-text-muted)] transition-colors hover:text-[var(--vw-text)]">
      &larr; 返回首页
    </a>

    <h1 class="font-body text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-[var(--vw-text)] sm:text-4xl">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[var(--vw-text-muted)]">Last updated: April 2025</p>

    <div class="mt-10">
      <!-- Acceptance -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--vw-text)] mt-10 mb-4">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-[var(--vw-text-secondary)] mb-4">
          By accessing or using VibeWeave ("the Service"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service ("Terms"). If you do not agree to these Terms, please do not use the Service. We reserve the right to modify these Terms at any time, and your continued use of the Service after modifications constitutes acceptance of the updated Terms.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Description of Service -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--vw-text)] mt-10 mb-4">2. Description of Service</h2>
        <p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-[var(--vw-text-secondary)] mb-4">
          VibeWeave is a music playlist analysis tool that fetches publicly available playlist data from third-party music platforms (such as NetEase Cloud Music), analyzes the emotional content of songs using AI, and presents the results in an interactive dashboard. The Service includes features for playlist visualization, emotion analysis, AI-powered song rearrangement, and custom tagging.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- User Accounts -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--vw-text)] mt-10 mb-4">3. User Accounts</h2>
        <p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-[var(--vw-text-secondary)] mb-4">
          To use certain features of the Service, you must create an account. You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account credentials and for all activities that occur under your account. You agree to notify us immediately of any unauthorized use of your account. You must be at least 13 years old to create an account.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- User Content -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--vw-text)] mt-10 mb-4">4. User Content & Playlist Data</h2>
        <p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-[var(--vw-text-secondary)] mb-4">
          When you add a playlist to VibeWeave, we fetch and store the playlist's song data (titles, artists, albums, lyrics) from the respective music platform. You retain no ownership rights over the fetched song data, as it belongs to the original rights holders. The analysis results generated by VibeWeave are provided for your personal, non-commercial use.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-[var(--vw-text-secondary)] mb-4">
          You agree not to:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 ml-6 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-[var(--vw-text-secondary)] mb-4">
          <li>Use the Service to distribute, reproduce, or publicly perform copyrighted song lyrics or music.</li>
          <li>Attempt to reverse-engineer, decompile, or disassemble any part of the Service.</li>
          <li>Use automated tools to scrape or extract data from the Service at scale.</li>
          <li>Interfere with or disrupt the integrity or performance of the Service.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <!-- Intellectual Property -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--vw-text)] mt-10 mb-4">5. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-[var(--vw-text-secondary)] mb-4">
          The VibeWeave application, including its code, design, logos, and documentation, is owned by us and protected by applicable intellectual property laws. Song lyrics, metadata, and other content fetched from third-party platforms remain the property of their respective rights holders. Our AI-generated analysis results are provided as a service and are not subject to copyright claims by either party.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Third-Party Content -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--vw-text)] mt-10 mb-4">6. Third-Party Content & Platforms</h2>
        <p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-[var(--vw-text-secondary)] mb-4">
          The Service relies on third-party music platforms (e.g., NetEase Cloud Music) to provide playlist and song data. We are not responsible for the availability, accuracy, or legality of content provided by these third parties. Your use of such third-party content is subject to the respective platform's terms of service. If a third-party platform changes its API or terms, some features of the Service may become unavailable.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Disclaimer -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--vw-text)] mt-10 mb-4">7. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
        <p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-[var(--vw-text-secondary)] mb-4">
          The Service is provided on an "as is" and "as available" basis without warranties of any kind, either express or implied. We do not guarantee that the Service will be uninterrupted, timely, secure, or error-free. The emotion analysis results are generated by AI and are subjective interpretations; they should not be considered definitive or used for professional purposes.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Limitation of Liability -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--vw-text)] mt-10 mb-4">8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-[var(--vw-text-secondary)] mb-4">
          To the fullest extent permitted by applicable law, we shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages arising out of or related to your use of the Service. Our total liability shall not exceed the amount you have paid to us in the twelve (12) months preceding the claim, or $100, whichever is greater.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Termination -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--vw-text)] mt-10 mb-4">9. Termination</h2>
        <p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-[var(--vw-text-secondary)] mb-4">
          We reserve the right to suspend or terminate your account and access to the Service at our sole discretion, without notice, for conduct that we believe violates these Terms or is harmful to other users, us, or third parties. Upon termination, your right to use the Service ceases immediately. Provisions that by their nature should survive termination shall remain in effect.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Governing Law -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--vw-text)] mt-10 mb-4">10. Governing Law</h2>
        <p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-[var(--vw-text-secondary)] mb-4">
          These Terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with applicable laws, without regard to conflict of law principles. Any disputes arising from these Terms or the Service shall be resolved through good-faith negotiation or, if necessary, in the courts of competent jurisdiction.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Contact -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--vw-text)] mt-10 mb-4">11. Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-[var(--vw-text-secondary)] mb-4">
          If you have any questions about these Terms, please contact us at <a href="mailto:legal@vibeweave.app" class="text-[var(--vw-accent)] hover:underline">legal@vibeweave.app</a>.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>

    <!-- Back to Home -->
    <div class="mt-12 border-t border-[var(--vw-border)] pt-8">
      <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full px-6 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium bg-[var(--vw-accent)] text-white hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity">
        返回首页
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>